\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{\sqrt{c+dx} - \sqrt{3}}{x} = \sqrt{3} 
\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{\sqrt{c+dx}-\sqrt{3}}{x}=\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{(\sqrt{c+dx}-\sqrt{3})(\sqrt{c+dx}+\sqrt{3})}{x(\sqrt{c+dx}+\sqrt{3})}=\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{c+dx-3}{x(\sqrt{c+dx}+\sqrt{3})}
